   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,369:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Real-Time Reddit Data Engineering Pipeline
   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,375:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Architecture
   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,379:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Reddit API (PRAW)  ──►  Kafka  ──►  Flink Processor  ──►  HDFS (Parquet)
