   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,651:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 10 — Access HDFS Web UI
   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,653:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Open in your browser:
   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,655:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
