   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,666:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : http://localhost:9864
   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,669:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 11 — Stop the pipeline
   DEBUG: 2026-02-18 23:15:15,672:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: # Stop all services (data is preserved)
